30:40.739 --> 30:41.707
Welcome, gentlemen.

30:41.707 --> 30:44.543
MARK SHIELDS: You're
welcome. Thank you.

30:44.543 --> 30:48.146
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, Benghazi
hearings, David, they went -- I
