31:11.570 --> 31:17.209
She -- her composure was
excellent. Congressmen do what
congressmen do. And so it was a
big

31:17.209 --> 31:23.048
nothing burger. And why the
Republicans remain obsessed with
this, at a time when the nation

31:23.048 --> 31:26.585
of Iraq has ceased to exist,
