that's what happened.

31:57.315 --> 32:01.386
JUDY WOODRUFF: They have
survived some challenges in the
past, the Clintons, but, Mark,
nothing

32:01.386 --> 32:03.388
burger, is that
what it adds up to?

32:03.388 --> 32:09.060
MARK SHIELDS: I would feel
better if it were just the
Clintons with the Republicans. I

32:09.060 --> 32:12.898
think this has been -- for the
past seven years of the Obama
administration, it has

32:12.898 --> 32:18.904
been an obsession that -- to
prove not simply that the
administration is not capable or

32:18.904 --> 32:24.342
efficient or effective, but that
somehow it's evil, maybe even
criminal.

32:24.342 --> 32:30.615
And that's what was driving this
Benghazi hearing, that somehow
that there was some

32:30.615 --> 32:37.989
evil plot or evil scheme or
diabolical whatever. The
emphasis on Sid Blumenthal, who
was a...

32:37.989 --> 32:41.326
JUDY WOODRUFF: Her
longtime friend.

32:41.326 --> 32:47.132
MARK SHIELDS: Yes, longtime
friend, controversial, a
conspiracy buff, an apparatchik,
whatever

32:47.132 --> 32:53.104
else he is, but, I mean, hardly
