hearing, which they didn't want

32:59.611 --> 33:02.013
to do. They looked
bad. They had...

33:02.013 --> 33:03.281
JUDY WOODRUFF: Meaning
the Republicans.

33:03.281 --> 33:07.018
MARK SHIELDS: The
Republicans looked bad.

33:07.018 --> 33:13.992
Hillary Clinton looked
disciplined. She showed
